704442f-b.title: Brooklyn: Franklin Avenue - Hancock Street
704442f-b.text:
Pranklin Avenue, at Hanchck Street. View 1 is south toward
Fulton Street, where the 'El" is.
View 2 ahows the Beford Branch of the Brooklyn Public Librery, facing Hancock street, and view 3 the Moose Lodae No. 14, adjoining the library.
P. L. Sperr  August 24, 1941
NO REPRODUCTIONE  Views 1-3
